\/2019\/09\/24\/ibn-abbas-mothers-best-deed\/","url_meta":{"origin":34790,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Mothers: Good to mothers best deed to draw near to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ata\u2019 ibn Yasar reported: A man came to Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, and he said, \u201cI proposed to a woman and she refused to marry me. Another man proposed to her and she was happy to marry him. I became jealous and I killed her. Is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31823,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/ibn-abbas-quran-whims\/","url_meta":{"origin":34790,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Whims: The Quran casts blame upon lowly desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Jawzi reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty did not mention whims in any place in his book but that he cast blame on it.\u201d Source: Dhamm al-Hawa\u0301 1\/36 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0648\u0632\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0630\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0632\u0651\u064e \u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5246,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/ibn-abbas-tafsir-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":34790,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tafsir: The Prophet prays for Ibn Abbas to understand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, put his hand on my shoulder and he said, \u201cO Allah, give him understanding in religion and teach him the interpretation of the Quran.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2879 Grade:\u00a0Qawi (strong) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34636,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/05\/best-deed-to-die-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34790,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Death: Best deed to die while remembering Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: I asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAmong which deeds are most beloved to Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat you die while your tongue is moist with the remembrance of Allah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 818 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0